#: ../../../news.rst:1363
msgid ""
"This release comes rather soon after 1.2.2 for one main reason: it was found "
"out that releases since 0.18 up to 1.2.2 (included) use some backported code "
"from Twisted (``scrapy.xlib.tx.*``), even if newer Twisted modules are "
"available. Scrapy now uses ``twisted.web.client`` and ``twisted.internet."
"endpoints`` directly. (See also cleanups below.)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:1370
msgid ""
"As it is a major change, we wanted to get the bug fix out quickly while not "
"breaking any projects using the 1.2 series."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:1376
